# grapher_explicit_parabola_smoke.numos — Phase 10B regression. Confirm the
# EXPLICIT y=x^2 still routes to the fast single-valued adaptive sampler after
# the implicit-equation classifier was added (LHS "y", RHS has no y → explicit).
# Warning-only (screenshot, no golden).
log "explicit parabola: start"
wait 200
open_app Grapher
wait 60
key down
key enter
# Type "y=x^2"
key y
key =
key x
key ^
key 2
key enter
wait 80
key graph
wait 80
key ac
key 0
wait 150
screenshot out/grapher_explicit_parabola_smoke.ppm
assert_app Grapher
log "explicit parabola: y=x^2 plotted"
